data.description: Gather with loved ones and friends at this Crystal Coast three-bedroom home. The coastal route to this home will take you to new adventures by the beaches and beyond.Seashells, remote beaches, ferry rides and islands with wild horses are minutes away from this home for you.  New carpet, new LVP, updated throughout the home, tucked away in a private community.  Hammocks Beach State Park is just around a 5-10 minute drive.  Come and schedule a tour of this inland home close to the water fun. Sellers willing to assist with Buyers closing costs.
